headline: Is Fastenal (FAST) Pricing Leave Enough Room After Strong Multi‑Year Share Gains
summary: If you are wondering whether Fastenal is fairly priced or if the market is getting ahead of itself, this article will walk you through what the numbers are really saying about the stock. Fastenal shares last closed at US$44.61, with returns of 5.2% over 7 days, 6.9% over 30 days, 10.3% year to date and 20.5% over 1 year, plus 94.4% over 3 years and 110.5% over 5 years that many investors will be trying to put into context.
